              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Minimum 720x720 pixels, JPG or PNG format. Use real product photography rather than stock imagery. Square or landscape composition crops best in the profile's product tab.</p></div></div>
